{"tid":1402472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"又有鬼，又內鬥，又唔散就係鬼","createTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:27.000Z","uid":180815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f9405cefce46e8d6e1586a72a7ca657f0bc6cd5f","tid":1402472,"uid":180815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:22:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我屌你老母，同14年有咩分別呀，衝就係鬼</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n各有各做唔係得個講字，有人想守，有人想be water係唔緊要<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>但唔好分化話係鬼，我地內鬥邊個最開心？</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n大家出黎就係戰友，鬼可能真係有，但自己會有獨立思考，我唔想大家出到黎係到疑神疑鬼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有想講多樣野<br />\n<br />\n企得前線唔該有心理準備，唔好人地一推就向後跑，真係會引發連鎖效應，你跑就個個跟住跑，狗就好易捉落單。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>你唔夠膽可以企後面，冇人怪你，量力而為，但上得前面，就係保護後面既人。</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n你跑走，身邊個個真係會比你害死。"},{"pid":"10c6eed56220c0175087a0308c9f4838afd4c3e9","tid":1402472,"uid":241244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不割蓆 不分化<br />\n明白大家唔同意見<br />\n呢篇野原意唔係反港獨<br />\n而係希望大家集中翻五大訴求</span></span><br />\n港獨？小心啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1400357\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1400357</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"465a12890abc82588a1c9d88b464905345a07a12","tid":1402472,"uid":180815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:26:43.000Z","msg":"不分化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84519ec7f9bd251de8246961cf3517df14efbaa8","tid":1402472,"uid":93998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:27:43.000Z","msg":"最好就拉撚晒班示威者 搞亂香港<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402145\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402145</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"48c13113fa6a51680d93fd74caa592cf591d3412","tid":1402472,"uid":233118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:39:23.000Z","msg":"全部人同我聽撚住 前線一就［撤退］一就［反擊］無死守呢條路<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402087\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402087</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b2b3bc198677b228e6b7afac30b06caf8aa3845d","tid":1402472,"uid":180815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T16:41:27.000Z","msg":"不分化！"}]}